text: Spark is the third studio album by Marit Larsen, released on 18 March 2011.November 2011 in Norway, Sweden, Finland and Denmark. It was also released on the 16th.December in Germany, Switzerland and Austria. The album contains ten songs, seven of which were written entirely by Marit Larsen herself. The first single from the album, "Coming Home", was released on 15th June.October. The second single, "Don't Move", was released on 30th June.January 2012.
title: Spark (Marit Larsen album)
